    "title": "Editing a package dependency as a local package"
  },
  "primaryContentSections": [
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "Overview",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "When you’re using a Swift package as a package dependency in your app, you may want",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "to make edits to it. For example, you may want to contribute a fix for a bug to an",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "open-source package. However, you can’t directly edit the content of a package dependency.",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "To make changes, add the Swift package as a local package to your app’s project.",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "Don’t remove your package dependency; adding a local package overrides the package",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "dependency with the same name. Xcode uses the package dependency again when you remove",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "the local package from your project.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "To add the Swift package as local package to your project:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Check out your package dependency’s source code from its Git repository.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Open your app’s Xcode project or workspace.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Choose File > Add Package Dependencies.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Click the Add Local button at the bottom of the package selection window.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Select the folder that contains your package and click the Add Package button.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Choose targets for the Package Products Xcode detects.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "type": "orderedList"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Now you can make changes to the local package and verify them by building and",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "running your app. When you’re done editing the local package, push your changes",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "to its remote Git repository. When the changes have made it into the package’s",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "next release, remove the local package from your project, and update the package",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "dependency to the new version.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
  ],
